The paper also discusses flaws in previous descriptions of the method and experimental demonstrations of Shor's algorithm, which could fall under the categories of computational complexity (cs.CC), cryptography and security (cs.CR), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and programming languages (cs.PL).
